OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CLovett
OL,6,FPeter Lovett, Age 99, Beach Unit
OL,8,FInterviewed 4 March 2024
OL,10,FLanding on Juno Beach in Normandy on D-
OL,11,FDay, Mr Lovett from Swanage was a
OL,12,Fmember of the Beach Units, crews whose
OL,13,Fjob was to keep soldiers and vehicles
OL,14,Fmoving once they had landed.
OL,16,FHe had undergone rigorous training in
OL,17,FStudland Bay and knew that a beach
OL,18,Fassault was imminent - but didn't know
OL,19,Fthe location.
