OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CLovett
OL,6,F"We had learnt everything from
OL,7,Fminelaying to mine lifting and
OL,8,Fabseiling down the cliffs at
OL,9,FBournemouth," he said.
OL,11,F"We were told we were training for
OL,12,Fassault landings and going in with
OL,13,Fassault troops and as it happened I
OL,14,Fwent in with the second wave.
OL,16,F"One day we got on the lorries and my
OL,17,Fcompany got into these landing ships.
OL,18,FThe crossing was rough. We were down
OL,19,Fbelow, they wouldn't allow us on deck.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
