OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CLovett
OL,6,F"We didn't know there were also
OL,7,FCanadian troops on board, and
OL,8,Feventually we came up on top and we
OL,9,Fhad to crouch along the side and then
OL,10,Fwe saw about a mile ahead was the
OL,11,Fbeach and you could hear shellfire and
OL,12,Fthings.
OL,14,F"I was very lucky.
OL,16,F"We came in at high tide and we were
OL,17,Funopposed there. So the first thing
OL,18,Fwas going up to our waist in water so
OL,19,Fwe were soaking wet.
