OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CLovett
OL,6,F"Then up to the sand dunes which we
OL,7,Fwere told were mined but we didn't
OL,8,Ffind many mines in the dunes at that
OL,9,Fstage."
OL,11,FBefore starting work Mr Lovett and his
OL,12,Fcolleagues were told to clear a nearby
OL,13,Fresidential area of enemy soldiers.
OL,15,F"There were dead bodies in the water,"
OL,16,FPeter added.
OL,18,F"We had to push the dead bodies away
OL,19,Fand there were bodies on the beach. I
OL,20,Fremember two pillboxes were still
OL,21,Ffiring at troops coming in.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
