OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CLovett
OL,6,F"Also we were there to clear mines
OL,7,Fwith the engineers who were really
OL,8,Fdoing it. We could hear machine guns
OL,9,Fin the distance but we never had
OL,10,Fgunfire there.
OL,12,F"There were prisoners who were being
OL,13,Fbrought down as well. It was a long
OL,14,Fday. You were wet through to start
OL,15,Fwith and it took two days to dry out."
OL,17,FThose manning the beaches were often
OL,18,Frequired around the clock.
