OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CLovett
OL,6,F"I remember at one time the beach
OL,7,Fbeing packed with vehicles and we
OL,8,Fcouldn't get them off," he said.
OL,10,F"We used to live off rations we had to
OL,11,Fscrounge off landing craft, including
OL,12,Fthe American ones. As soon as the last
OL,13,Fvehicle drove off the ramp went up and
OL,14,Fthey reversed out.
OL,16,F"They didn't hang about. And you used
OL,17,Fto have to rush on, ask them for
OL,18,Fration packs and run off before they
OL,19,Fpulled out."
